excerpt.rendered:
The Bullit 470 outboard with M.O.B. certification. The lightweight aluminium tender boat is 4.70m long and 1.75m wide. The draft is 0.20m and the vertical clearance 1.15m. The hull weight of the Bullit 470 is 300kg.
